query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('asp.net-mvc-3',
'batch-file',
'caching',
'collections',
'concurrency',
'email',
'file-io',
'functional-programming',
'hash',
'java-8',
'testing',
'video')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Census',
'Editor',
'Excavator',
'Explainer',
'Great Answer',
'Informed',
'Nice Question',
'Notable Question',
'Organizer',
'Popular Question',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Yearling') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
